{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/1772602275858/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602276960", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/1772602275858/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602276960"}, "identifier": "d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（1）本题考查的是对诗歌意思的理解。ABC．正确；D．有误，《茅屋为秋风所破歌》中的&ldquo;安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士供欢颜，风雨不动安如山。呜呼！何时眼前突兀见此屋，吾庐独破受冻死亦足&rdquo;运用的是直接抒情和议论的表达方式。故选：D</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面这首诗理解有误的一项是（　　）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>茅屋为秋风所破歌 &nbsp;杜甫</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。茅飞渡江洒江郊，高者挂罥长林梢，下者飘转沉塘坳。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>南村群童欺我老无力，忍能对面为盗贼。公然抱茅入竹去，唇焦口燥呼不得，归来倚杖自叹息。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。布衾多年冷似铁，娇儿恶卧踏里裂。床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。自经丧乱少睡眠，长夜沾湿何由彻！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜！风雨不动安如山。呜呼！何时眼前突兀见此屋，吾庐独破受冻死亦足！</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "对下面这首诗理解有误的一项是（　　）茅屋为秋风所破歌  杜甫八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。茅飞渡江洒江郊，高者挂罥长林梢，下者飘转沉塘坳。南村群童欺我老无力，忍能对面为盗贼。公然抱茅入竹去，唇焦口燥呼不得，归来倚杖自叹息。俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。布衾多年冷似铁，娇儿恶卧踏里裂。床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。自经丧乱少睡眠，长夜沾湿何由彻！安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜！风雨不动安如", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/item.json?v=1720576692771", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这首诗是杜甫因所住茅屋被秋风吹破引发感慨而写下的脍炙人口的不朽诗篇。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>诗人对南村群童公然抱茅逃进竹林的行为无可奈何，只好拄杖归来，独自叹息。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>布衾如铁，屋漏床湿，雨脚如麻，长夜难眠，表现出诗人穷困苦痛的生活状况。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这首诗最后一段运用叙述、抒情的表达方式，表现了诗人忧国忧民的济世情怀。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面这首诗理解有误的一项是（　　）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>茅屋为秋风所破歌 &nbsp;杜甫</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。茅飞渡江洒江郊，高者挂罥长林梢，下者飘转沉塘坳。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>南村群童欺我老无力，忍能对面为盗贼。公然抱茅入竹去，唇焦口燥呼不得，归来倚杖自叹息。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。布衾多年冷似铁，娇儿恶卧踏里裂。床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。自经丧乱少睡眠，长夜沾湿何由彻！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜！风雨不动安如山。呜呼！何时眼前突兀见此屋，吾庐独破受冻死亦足！</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "对下面这首诗理解有误的一项是（　　）茅屋为秋风所破歌  杜甫八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。茅飞渡江洒江郊，高者挂罥长林梢，下者飘转沉塘坳。南村群童欺我老无力，忍能对面为盗贼。公然抱茅入竹去，唇焦口燥呼不得，归来倚杖自叹息。俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。布衾多年冷似铁，娇儿恶卧踏里裂。床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。自经丧乱少睡眠，长夜沾湿何由彻！安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜！风雨不动安如"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面这首诗理解有误的一项是（　　）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>茅屋为秋风所破歌 &nbsp;杜甫</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>八月秋高风怒号，卷我屋上三重茅。茅飞渡江洒江郊，高者挂罥长林梢，下者飘转沉塘坳。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>南村群童欺我老无力，忍能对面为盗贼。公然抱茅入竹去，唇焦口燥呼不得，归来倚杖自叹息。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>俄顷风定云墨色，秋天漠漠向昏黑。布衾多年冷似铁，娇儿恶卧踏里裂。床头屋漏无干处，雨脚如麻未断绝。自经丧乱少睡眠，长夜沾湿何由彻！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜！风雨不动安如山。呜呼！何时眼前突兀见此屋，吾庐独破受冻死亦足！</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "unpack", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/1772602275858/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602276960", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/1772602275858/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602276960"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2024", "nature": "tm_sync", "audit_teacher_ids": ["0bae06d7-5d63-4add-9d62-6848880cbc43"], "version_source_id": "d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a", "format": "2d641585-d91b-4d65-8f5a-2a7fd8103ac7", "faculty_advisor_ids": ["0d011f6a-8dcb-4adb-8f5b-13c5783254be"], "teacher_ids": ["cafeac00-17c3-401a-93ca-a93e34c858a9"], "audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "sys_resource_space": 395675, "thumbnail_audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "qb_qu_num": 4, "qb_knowledge_points": ["课内阅读"], "res_sort": 202407100942464, "size": 193900, "produce_type": "artificiality", "thumbnails": ["cs_path:${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/1772602275858/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602277096"], "providers": ["38a5579d-96c6-436f-a3f6-9cea33e5e3be"], "sys_packing_result": {}}, "resource_type_code": "questions", "ti_items": [{"ti_md5": "2724343c158bef9d0a4e8fbc1099e8cf", "ti_res_version": null, "ti_format": "json", "ti_size": 4055, "ti_storage": "cs_path:${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/item.json?v=1720576692771", "ti_file_flag": "href", "ti_is_source_file": true, "custom_properties": null, "ti_printable": false, "lc_ti_format": "xml"}, {"ti_md5": "3a362fe1082a741b4a7da3bea19f592f", "ti_res_version": null, "ti_format": "xml", "ti_size": 317, "ti_storage": "cs_path:${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/questions/d0a7899e-c361-46b6-8c8c-3876a1720b5a.pkg/main.xml?v=1720576693326", "ti_file_flag": "nd_href", "ti_is_s